00:56:49,450 --> 00:56:54,528
Speaker 0: "Inawashishiro Kamehamehasama has sent the meat of a renowned bushi from Izumono Kuni from View to

809
00:56:54,608 --> 00:56:55,029
Speaker 0: enjoy.".

