00:57:46,991 --> 00:57:49,370
Speaker 0: They're using Dynamic Equivalence from what I've seen.

824
00:57:50,094 --> 00:57:52,930
Speaker 0: I put a couple of examples in the video.

825
00:57:53,410 --> 00:58:01,230
Speaker 0: I mean, Bollywood especially, there's loads of honorifics in Hindi and various other Indian languages.

826
00:58:02,331 --> 00:58:06,610
Speaker 0: And we were watching a few Bollywood films recently and they're all just localized.

827
