Speaker 0: It says Dad.

830
00:58:13,576 --> 00:58:15,610
Speaker 0: So it's Dynamic Equivalence pretty much all the way.

831
00:58:15,710 --> 00:58:25,090
Speaker 0: There's a French film called Just Visiting with the really cool guy Jean Renaud.

832
00:58:26,231 --> 00:58:28,161
Speaker 0: I think it's Jean Renaud.

