1039
01:12:31,598 --> 01:12:36,810
Speaker 0: A lot of the game translation, in fact, all of the game translation work I get is in Excel format.

1040
01:12:37,410 --> 01:12:40,096
Speaker 0: And you've got a character limit that you have to stick to.

1041
01:12:40,117 --> 01:12:45,750
Speaker 0: And often, on the left is the Japanese and on the right is the space for you to write your English translation.

1042
01:12:46,171 --> 01:12:54,810
Speaker 0: And on the left, you've got a five kanji compound, which means super spinning, multipart, deathblow, super special attack.

1043
01:12:55,150 --> 01:12:58,180
Speaker 0: And you've got to get that in 10 characters.

1044
01:12:58,521 --> 01:12:59,283
Speaker 0: And it's impossible.

