1058
01:14:35,373 --> 01:14:37,630
Speaker 0: So yeah, definitely a couple of languages you can do.

1059
01:14:38,091 --> 01:14:48,389
Speaker 1: Alright, so I don't know if you want to talk about this, but you do this professionally, do you want to talk about exactly which projects you've worked on, maybe some you're really proud of or anything like that?

1060
01:14:50,111 --> 01:15:04,170
Speaker 0: Right, the trouble we're working with games and novels like I do is that you've got your non-disclosure agreement which you have to sign, and so you can only really talk about it when the game or the novel is released on the shelves.

1061
01:15:04,811 --> 01:15:17,990
Speaker 0: But especially with novels, I mean, the first novels I translated for Del Rey, or was it someone else, I think, the first ones I did like two years ago, and they're still not on the shelves.

1062
01:15:19,430 --> 01:15:20,192
