Speaker 0: rates?".

1075
01:16:24,782 --> 01:16:27,529
Speaker 0: And I was like, "Oh, it's this much per

1076
01:16:27,569 --> 01:16:27,829
Speaker 0: word.".

1077
01:16:28,170 --> 01:16:32,529
Speaker 0: And they sent back and said, "That's 300 times more than what we pay our normal

1078
01:16:32,549 --> 01:16:32,750
Speaker 0: people.".

